ai-cyber-risk-platform/
├── data/                  # Example: security_logs/, threat_feeds/, business_events/
├── processed/             # Cleaned and enriched datasets
├── models/                # Trained AI/ML models (e.g., risk_scorer.pkl)
├── notebooks/             # EDA, model tuning, business impact simulation
│   ├── eda.ipynb
│   └── business_impact.ipynb
├── src/                   # Core Python modules
│   ├── ingest.py
│   ├── risk_scoring.py
│   ├── business_impact.py
│   ├── dashboard.py
│   ├── recommend.py
│   └── utils.py
├── dashboards/            # Dashboard screenshots, configs, exports
├── docs/                  # Project documentation
├── requirements.txt       # Python dependencies
└── README.md              # Project overview, setup, usage, business highlights
